{"tid":2506044,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"耳機品牌 — Lear樂耳員工/老細態度西過狗","createTime":"2021-04-27T05:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T22:27:07.000Z","uid":52712,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad3291e4082801b3145f4cd3083183931cd6a80","tid":2506044,"uid":52712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"上年貪平係佢到買左個cm耳機 我唔係到評論佢音質 造工果啲<br />\n2月收完貨 番去試果時有一邊覺得唔太岩位, <br />\n咁我就拎番去refit(我總共refit左<span class=\"red\">3</span>次, 整完係無任何分別, <span class=\"red\">都係同一個人幫我搞</span> 唔知佢係老細定員工) 每次去到佢都係西哂面 好唔情願理我咁<br />\n同佢講完邊個位唔岩 邊度有啲頂住 佢次次聽完就算 無回應 之後就用marker求其markup一個位hea9我。 <br />\n次次山長水遠黎拎比你整再番黎拎，仲要貼錢比你西我面，呼籲大家下次買耳機果時切勿貪平中伏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有次想順便買個耳膠 我比左個耳機佢睇 問邊款岩size 我怕會套唔到入去。佢答我隻隻都差唔多 自己睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果老細見到呢個po, 果個係你員工既話 麻煩比多啲training佢 改善下佢呢啲西口西面既態道 , after-sale service 試下認真少少.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYGoPWDFgxHwXe9UA9bScaFGjjyBfzp3wjBFn6B5h7FzS?filename=VJh1Q7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJh1Q7A.jpg&h=33aecf4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e72b05e974c47d1db64e98b13d7052028995f0f9","tid":2506044,"uid":319092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"你買咗邊對"},{"pid":"a8dee472608f2cf46b9746644f43abd90e6e31d7","tid":2506044,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"$0wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />where貼錢"},{"pid":"7e9274c54977b5828099b6bca4d60d4af2b72517","tid":2506044,"uid":185184,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"lear出哂名架啦bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a6382e5834dd2ea00322f16f74126adb86930b","tid":2506044,"uid":253159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e9274c54977b5828099b6bca4d60d4af2b72